<li id="cite_note-5"><b><a href="#cite_ref-5" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal">Boscá Díaz-Pintado, María C. (29-31 March 2007). "<a href="http://philsci-archive.pitt.edu/archive/00003568/" class="external text" title="http://philsci-archive.pitt.edu/archive/00003568/" rel="nofollow">Updating the wave-particle duality</a>". <i>15th UK and European Meeting on the Foundations of Physics</i>. <span class="reference-accessdate">Retrieved on <span class="mw-formatted-date" title="2008-06-21"><a href="/wiki/2008" title="2008">2008</a>-<a href="/wiki/June_21" title="June 21">06-21</a></span></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=proceeding&amp;rft.btitle=15th+UK+and+European+Meeting+on+the+Foundations+of+Physics&amp;rft.atitle=Updating+the+wave-particle+duality&amp;rft.aulast=Bosc%C3%A1+D%C3%ADaz-Pintado&amp;rft.aufirst=Mar%C3%ADa+C.&amp;rft.date=29-31+March+2007&amp;rft.place=Leeds%2C+UK&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fphilsci-archive.pitt.edu%2Farchive%2F00003568%2F"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
